{"tid":1890053,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"昨日因 今日果 淺談社會現況","createTime":"2020-02-21T03:13:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T00:27:34.000Z","uid":74778,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e963777abdaeebc11e3db0dfb17776a4ee7067cc","tid":1890053,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T03:13:31.000Z","msg":"其實屈埋喺心好耐，明明係好簡單直接，但次次同朋友傾親就好容易就沈迷咗喺一兩個問題上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由晚清開始，鬼佬入黎中國係做生意，根本唔會care你邊個執政、人權係點。佢地會因為你人權問題而出手打你，打你都係貪你有搵錢價值。<br />\n<br />\n當年有李鴻章做白手套，瘋狂賣國賠地，自己喺中間抽水。今日中國有香港做白手套，所有法律隙野都係喺香港走。<span style=\"color: blue;\">香港嘅價值係喺呢到，咁先搵到錢。</span><br />\n<br />\n到毛澤東睇完馬克思啲野睇到㷫烚烚，搞咗個共產黨出黎，<span style=\"color: blue;\">...農民、無知識嘅無產階級，上位執政，熱烈擁護佢地信奉嘅唯物主義、無神主義，再加上批鬥儒學同知識份子，中國一下子所有道德觀念無曬</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">重點黎</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n二戰後，世界各地都出現一種<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">重振經濟</span></strong>嘅論調，即係1945年後嘅<span style=\"color: blue;\">現代主義中心思想</span>，當時嘅<em>日本 德國 意大利 美國 蘇俄(冷戰 軍備競賽 都加速咗經濟同科競發展)</em>，全部都大力投入人力物力各方面嘅資源，去振興返國力。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">唯獨中國...</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1945年中國打完抗日戰，日本返屋企，<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>毛澤東好戰</strong></span>，繼續同蔣介石打，打多4年，到1949年，中共國成立，後生過中華民國38歲。<br />\n<br />\n之後就係毛澤東統治惡夢之始<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">人地用戰後幾十年時間，去振興自己國家經濟，強大自己國力！人地呢個思潮，係一班人，不約而同地、因應世界氣候，去適應出黎，喺適當時候做適當嘅野..<br />\n佢老母臭閪個毛澤東，用幾十年時間三反、五反、鎮反、土改、肅反、反右、文革、大躍進...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/92JqQCT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F92JqQCT.jpg&h=b246aa62&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qEgjU4y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqEgjU4y.jpg&h=f332d901&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.epochtimes.com/b5/14/5/8/n4149940.htm/amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F14%2F5%2F8%2Fn4149940.htm%2Famp&d=8qD7g5vOfNqkLkogRxTPVNAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=37948c3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.epochtimes.com/b5/14/5/8/n4149940.htm/amp</a><br />\n呢段歷史真係睇到人好撚心嗡，成個故仔係錯撚曬<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n到今日，有時同啲藍親戚傾開傾，佢地好自豪宜家自己國家有錢，一比人話<em>土豪 無文化...</em>，就會反駁 <em><strong>阿藍，以前中國人餓咗好耐，你未經歷過你唔明嫁啦</strong></em>，我心諗 佢自己攞黎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1. 大家有個概念係戰後各國重視<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">經濟 資源 物質</span></strong>，<br />\n2. 而中國係<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">喺到</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">戇鳩 喺到柒 喺到搞權力鬥爭</span></strong>，就ok。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">真&bull;重點</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">到咗21世紀，各國嘅人民浸淫喺戰後豐富嘅物質盛宴幾十年，下一代或者下兩代嘅人(即係宜家2 30歲嘅人)，已經對物質麻木，過度嘅物質生活做成審美疲勞，</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n美國<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.netflix.com/title/80114460?s=i&amp;trkid=13747225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.netflix.com%2Ftitle%2F80114460%3Fs%3Di%26trkid%3D13747225&d=8qD7g5vOfNqkLkogRxTPVNAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=e54c705e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.netflix.com/title/80114460?s=i&amp;trkid=13747225</a><br />\n<br />\n日本<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/断舍离\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E6%96%AD%E8%88%8D%E7%A6%BB&d=8qD7g5vOfNqkLkogRxTPVNAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=76f34b86\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/断舍离</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>各國嘅人都興起追求精神生活，健康生活，經濟唔係最重要，因為有錢都唔一定快樂。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">唯獨中國...</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共對思想同資訊箝制，中國人一直嘅精神生活都停留喺1954年，無行前過，只係不斷將1954年自己嘅唯物慾望，瘋狂咁加深...<br />\n<br />\n所以宜家佢好似當年英國殖民時代咁，搞一帶一路，債務殖民。又莽顧安全環保等可持續性因素，做世界工廠，令本土生態受嚴重且不可逆轉嘅破壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當國際社會不斷咁行前:<br />\n由戰後大搞貿易經濟，到今天重視精神生活，<br />\n世界行嘅每一步都反映中國嘅落後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff6d0b77c7d60c5fbfdee6ad053a66437c5f1ff7","tid":1890053,"uid":198773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T09:33:58.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"bd281643819652b93a679684d23785e70e1b9c5c","tid":1890053,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T00:21:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5b61412b5ef05fa3bbf8296f37f3a33a42091b1","tid":1890053,"uid":124899,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T00:31:05.000Z","msg":"下﹖<br />\n乜將條死氣喉塞左過對面屋就等於你無開冷氣﹖<br />\n中國係工廠呀，但啲野邊撚個用架﹖<br />\n咩極簡主義&hellip;我屌，實行既人都唔知有無1%。<br />\n咁都攞黎丁。<br />\n<br />\n最撚鍾意以公司業積用錢生錢<br />\n最撚貪既果啲仆街響華爾街<br />\n<br />\n等睇人話我五毛。"},{"pid":"afed41cf95ccd02f5dbadf9f744e06a4430101a7","tid":1890053,"uid":124899,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T00:39:13.000Z","msg":"睇吓炭排放先喇<br />\n一般人會話中國美國係全球排得最勁&hellip;<br />\n但，佢地唔會提，你只係開左冷氣但個死氣喉放左去中國<br />\n<br />\n正常人會睇依個表<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zg084eR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzg084eR.jpg&h=f8098f4f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nSOURCE：<a href=\"https://www.pnas.org/content/107/12/5687\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pnas.org%2Fcontent%2F107%2F12%2F5687&d=8qD7g5vOfNqkLkogRxTPVNAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=dc5cb11b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pnas.org/content/107/12/5687</a><br />\n正正因為佢係「世界工廠」其實好多製成成品所用到既排放<br />\n根本就唔應該入中國數<br />\n<br />\n再睇返依個圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Qr0Vnb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Qr0Vnb.jpg&h=4b535f26&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n就明白樓主已經講緊廢話。<br />\n睇返第三行，就大約可以知道乜野國家先係最物質主義。"},{"pid":"339e3a760cbcab5cb1ff6ca56f8a1ddebad3e15c","tid":1890053,"uid":124899,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T00:43:32.000Z","msg":"我地係人頭計第七位浪費呀。反省左自己先喇"},{"pid":"1e14979f861cfa1ed683e5d06592e3946335a9b0","tid":1890053,"uid":50525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T01:04:04.000Z","msg":"LM<br />\n少有連登高登post"},{"pid":"32e3819f4224464179a5d0d70f9583ab572e2ac8","tid":1890053,"uid":74778,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"afed41cf95ccd02f5dbadf9f744e06a4430101a7","tid":1890053,"uid":124899,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T00:39:13.000Z","msg":"睇吓炭排放先喇<br />\n一般人會話中國美國係全球排得最勁&hellip;<br />\n但，佢地唔會提，你只係開左冷氣但個死氣喉放左去中國<br />\n<br />\n正常人會睇依個表<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zg084eR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzg084eR.jpg&h=f8098f4f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nSOURCE：<a href=\"https://www.pnas.org/content/107/12/5687\" data-sr-url=\"